original_title: The Delightful Sausage: Nowt But Sea
overview: The biggest-titted Edinburgh Best Show nominees return in their darkest-ever adventure. Learn the horrifying true story of what happened when Amy and Christopher-Louise decided to hide from their problems on a remote island. As tensions flare and psyches fray, how will Yorkshire's finest meat-themed duo survive?
title: The Delightful Sausage: Nowt But Sea
